[
{ type: install
  message: <<EOM
OpenBao Agent has been installed.

To configure the agent:

1. Copy the sample configuration:
   cp %%PREFIX%%/etc/bao-agent.hcl.sample %%PREFIX%%/etc/bao-agent.hcl

2. Place your AppRole credentials in %%BAOSECRETDIR%%/:
   - role-id   (from: bao read auth/approle/role/<role>/role-id)
   - secret-id (from: bao write -f auth/approle/role/<role>/secret-id)

   Ensure correct ownership and permissions:
   chown %%USER%%:%%GROUP%% %%BAOSECRETDIR%%/role-id %%BAOSECRETDIR%%/secret-id
   chmod 600 %%BAOSECRETDIR%%/role-id %%BAOSECRETDIR%%/secret-id

3. Enable and start the agent:
   sysrc openbao_agent_enable=YES
   service openbao_agent start

The agent writes its token to /var/run/bao/token (mode 0600).

A sample Monit configuration is installed at:
%%PREFIX%%/share/examples/openbao-agent/openbao_agent.monit
EOM
}
]
